author: COMSOL
description: This example models discharge of a lithium-sulfur battery cell at two different discharge rates. The electrolyte charge and mass transport of a lithium salt and six polysulfides is included, as well as the precipitation-dissolution of solid octasulfur (S8) and lithium sulfide (Li2S) in the separator and positive electrode.
